<doc id="1024407" wikidata="Q3266619" url="?curid=1024407" title="H-Wonder">
<text>H-Wonder is a Japanese music arranger and composer. He debuted in 1995. In June 1998, he stopped being a solo artist and changed his name to H-Wonder and became a composer. One of his notable collaborations is with Maaya Sakamoto and BoA.

