==Greatest ever team==
After some debate during March 2011, the Rotherham Titans fans voted for a greatest ever team of players and coaching staff. The fans decided on:
* 15 Bernardo Stortoni
* 14 David Strettle
* 13 Kevin Maggs
* 12 Mike Umaga
* 11 Errie Claassens
* 10 Ramiro Pez
* 9 Dave Scully
* 8 Mike Schmid (captain)
* 7 Hendre Fourie
* 6 Craig West
* 5 John Dudley
* 4 Glen Kenworthy
* 3 Colin Noon
* 2 Chris Johnson
* 1 Carl Banks
* Coach: Jim Kilfoyle
* Captain: Mike Schmid

A further survey carried out in 2023 concluded that Carl Banks was voted the single greatest every player to grace Clifton Lane. 

